---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Heritage — Global Faith Temple"
  description="The history, culture, and legacy of Global Faith Temple — held in remembrance, entrusted with care."
>
  <main>

    <header class="relative bg-ivory pb-16 pt-40 md:pb-24 md:pt-48">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center">
        <p class="fade-up mb-6 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-olive opacity-80">Heritage</p>
        <h1 class="fade-up font-serif text-4xl leading-[1.1] text-olive-deep md:text-6xl">
          What is carried,<br />what is kept.
        </h1>
        <p class="fade-up mx-auto mt-8 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed md:text-lg" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.78);">
          The temple was founded in remembrance — built upon one man's whole inheritance, given freely so that the soldiers of Vietnam and her seven allies might be honored together. Its history, its culture, and the legacy we hope to leave are bound by a single thread: gratitude.
        </p>
        <div class="fade-up mt-12 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 text-olive opacity-50">
          <span class="h-px w-10" style="background: rgba(74,76,33,0.4);"></span>
          <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10"><circle cx="5" cy="5" r="1.4" fill="currentColor" /></svg>
          <span class="h-px w-10" style="background: rgba(74,76,33,0.4);"></span>
        </div>
        <nav class="fade-up mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-olive opacity-70">
          <a href="#history" class="hover:text-olive">History</a><span class="opacity-30">·</span>
          <a href="#culture" class="hover:text-olive">Culture</a><span class="opacity-30">·</span>
          <a href="#legacy" class="hover:text-olive">Legacy</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- History -->
    <section id="history" class="scroll-mt-24 border-t py-20 md:py-28" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.1);">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="reveal-left md:col-span-4">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-olive opacity-70">History</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-olive-deep md:text-4xl">A story begun in quiet rooms.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right md:col-span-8 space-y-5 text-[17px] leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.82);">
          <p>
            Global Faith Temple began with a single conviction held by its founder: that the soldiers of the Republic of Vietnam — and of every nation that stood beside them — must not be allowed to fade from memory. He had lived through the war as a young man. He had counted the cost.
          </p>
          <p>
            For decades, he gathered what he could. When the time was right, he gave it all — every parcel of land his family had kept, every saving of his working years — to build a sanctuary where service, sacrifice, and faith could be held together: neither glorified nor forgotten.
          </p>
          <p>
            From a borrowed hall to our present sanctuary, the growth has been slow and chosen. Each step taken by those willing to stay long enough to see it through.
          </p>
          <ul class="stagger mt-6 space-y-4">
            <li class="fade-up flex gap-6 border-t pt-3" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">
              <span class="w-20 shrink-0 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive">1998</span>
              <span style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">First gatherings of veterans and families, in a borrowed community hall.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up flex gap-6 border-t pt-3" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">
              <span class="w-20 shrink-0 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive">2001</span>
              <span style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">Our founder pledges his land and assets to the future of the temple.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up flex gap-6 border-t pt-3" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">
              <span class="w-20 shrink-0 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive">2003</span>
              <span style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">The sanctuary is dedicated; the first candle is lit at daybreak and has not gone out since.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up flex gap-6 border-t pt-3" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">
              <span class="w-20 shrink-0 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive">2010</span>
              <span style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">Partnerships begin with sister communities in Huế, Đà Nẵng, and Hồ Chí Minh City.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up flex gap-6 border-t pt-3" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">
              <span class="w-20 shrink-0 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive">2015</span>
              <span style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">The roll of remembrance is formally extended to all seven allied nations.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up flex gap-6 border-t pt-3" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">
              <span class="w-20 shrink-0 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive">2019</span>
              <span style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">The Council of Stewards is established, to carry the founder's charter forward.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="fade-up flex gap-6 border-t pt-3" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">
              <span class="w-20 shrink-0 font-serif text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive">Today</span>
              <span style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.85);">An open door, every day of the year. A candle, every dawn.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Culture -->
    <section id="culture" class="scroll-mt-24 border-t py-20 md:py-28" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.1); background-color: var(--parchment);">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="reveal-left md:col-span-4">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-olive opacity-70">Culture</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-olive-deep md:text-4xl">How we hold one another, day by day.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right md:col-span-8 space-y-5 text-[17px] leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.82);">
          <p>
            Our culture is shaped by small habits: a candle tended each morning, a meal shared each week, a moment of silence kept at the start of every gathering, and a single name spoken aloud — for a soldier, somewhere, on someone's behalf.
          </p>
          <p>
            We speak softly of difficult things and gently of one another. We give time as the most honest gift we know how to offer.
          </p>
          <div class="stagger mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="fade-up border-l pl-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-base text-olive-deep">Silence</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">We begin and end in stillness. The noise of the world waits outside.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-l pl-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-base text-olive-deep">Hospitality</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">There is always a chair, a cup of tea, and a moment for whoever has come.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-l pl-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-base text-olive-deep">Honesty</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">We name what is true with care. No story is sweetened, and no grief is hurried.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Legacy -->
    <section id="legacy" class="scroll-mt-24 border-t py-20 md:py-28" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.1);">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="reveal-left md:col-span-4">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-olive opacity-70">Legacy</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-olive-deep md:text-4xl">What we hope to leave behind.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right md:col-span-8">
          <div class="grid items-center gap-10 md:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="relative aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden rounded-sm">
              <img src="/assets/remembrance-candle.jpg" alt="A single lit candle beside an olive branch" loading="lazy" class="h-full w-full object-cover candle-flicker" />
              <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(53,54,23,0.4), transparent 60%);"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-5 text-[17px] leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.82);">
              <p>
                A community that remembers the cost of peace, and tends to that peace as a daily practice rather than a distant ideal.
              </p>
              <p>
                An archive of letters, names, and quiet stories from the families of all eight nations — so that those who come after us inherit not only walls and rituals, but living memory.
              </p>
              <p>
                A temple our founder never asked to be named for. He gave everything, and asked only that the candle never go out.
              </p>
              <p class="font-serif italic text-olive">
                "We are tenants of the temple, never its owners."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Base>
